REPORT
  Show a diplomatic and activity report for all nations.

SYNTAX
  report [<cnum>]
  repo   [<cnum>]

DESCRIPTION
  Lists active nations with their current status, relations to you,
  and recent activity timestamps.

  Displays:
    - Country number and name
    - Your current relation to each country
    - Their relation toward you
    - Last login time
    - Approximate military and economic power indicators

  Without an argument, shows all active nations.

EXAMPLE
  report                    see all countries
  report 3                  see just country 3's report

SEE ALSO
  relations  declare  power  nation  telegram
